Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.54,0:00:05.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{Hey! Kirie!}Này Kirie!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.17,0:00:12.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{The hell? Where did she run off to?}Con bé chạy đi đâu rồi?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.79,0:00:16.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{Well, whatever. I've got nothing to do,\Nand I'm broke after going shopping yesterday.}Mà dù sao mình cũng rảnh,\N hôm qua mua đồ hết tiền nữa...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.13,0:00:19.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{Maybe I'll just go to Taihei's place...}Chắc qua chỗ Taihei vậy.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.50,0:00:28.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{These custard cakes sure are yummy!}Bánh này ngon ghê! \N(Trans: choux cream)
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.79,0:00:31.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{Yes! And there are still plenty more left!}Ừm! Vẫn còn nhiều đó!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.63,0:00:35.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{Thank you, Kirie.}Cảm ơn em nhé Kirie.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.58,0:00:40.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{No, I don't know why, but these were just\Nlying around the house. So please, go ahead.}Không có gì đâu ạ. Chỉ là \Nem vô tình thấy chúng ở nhà thôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.58,0:00:43.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Huh? She "didn't know why"?}Vô tình thấy chúng ở nhà?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.79,0:00:45.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{Oh! That's incredible, Master!}Tuyệt ghê Sư phụ!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.54,0:00:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Kinh chưa này! Hey hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.00,0:00:49.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{That's just rude!}Này, cấm chơi với thức ăn!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.71,0:00:53.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{Huh? Who's that?}Ủa, ai vậy nhỉ?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.75,0:00:54.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{Coming!}Ra ngay!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.96,0:00:59.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{Dude, it's REALLY cold out here. Hurry up and let me in!}Ở ngoài lạnh lắm.\N Cho tôi vào nhanh nào!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.13,0:01:01.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{Huh?}Ủa?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.75,0:01:05.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{Ah! Kirie!}Kirie?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.79,0:01:10.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{Hey! Those are the custard cakes I bought yesterday!}Đó là bánh anh mua hôm qua mà!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.96,0:01:18.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{I was looking forward to eating those tonight...}Anh định tận hưởng chúng vào tối nay...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.13,0:01:21.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{So she basically thieved them, huh?}Em ấy tự mang nó đi à?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.25,0:03:04.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{This has gotten sort of awkward, hasn't it?}Trông có vẻ không ổn nhỉ?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.00,0:03:07.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{Even though they're brother and sister, yeah...}Cho dù họ có là anh em đi nữa ...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.42,0:03:14.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{Oh, hey.}Ra vậy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.83,0:03:17.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{You're always coming here to hang out, aren't you?}Em luôn qua đây chơi đúng không?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.46,0:03:21.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{It's good that you haven't just been staying home alone.}Cũng tốt vì dù sao em luôn ở nhà một mình.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.21,0:03:26.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{I'm glad that you've made a good friend.}May mà em có 1 người bạn tốt.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.83,0:03:32.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{Yeah!}Ừm!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.79,0:03:37.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{And thanks for those custard cakes, Bomba!}Cảm ơn anh vì chỗ bánh nhé Bomba!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.58,0:03:41.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{Huh? Well, I bought them for Kirie anyway.}Mà dù sao anh cũng mua chúng cho Kirie mà.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.88,0:03:43.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{Let me get you some cola to say thanks!}Cola để cảm ơn anh nè!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.83,0:03:45.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{Ooh! Thanks, Tanukichi.}Cảm ơn nhé Tanukichi.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.75,0:03:48.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{T-Tanu...kichi?}T-Tanu...kichi?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.83,0:03:53.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{I mean, she looks like a tanuki, right? So, "Tanukichi."}Thì em ấy trông giống tanuki đúng không?\NNên anh mới gọi là Tanukichi.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.67,0:03:59.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{You call my Master a TANUKI?!}Anh gọi Sư phụ là Tanuki?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.83,0:04:05.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{If you see my Master's cuteness and think\Nthat she's a tanuki, something is wrong with you!}Anh coi sự dễ thương của Sư phụ \Nnhư tanuki, anh có làm sao không vậy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.38,0:04:07.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{Well, they look sort of the same, don't they?}Nhưng...giống thật mà?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.46,0:04:08.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{THEY DO NOT!}Không giống!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.42,0:04:13.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{If anything, it's weird that you call her "Master."}Nếu có gì lạ, thì đó là việc \Nem gọi em ấy là Sư phụ đấy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.08,0:04:16.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{A master of friggin' what?}Sư phụ về cái gì mới được chứ?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.00,0:04:23.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{L-look! What makes you think\Nyou have to worry about the friends I keep?!}T-Tại sao anh phải quan tâm tới bạn em chứ?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.54,0:04:27.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{I had a good time when we were at the beach,\Nwithout you being around.}Em đã có khoảng thời gian\N vui vẻ ở bãi biển, khi không có anh.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.50,0:04:30.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{You didn't even pay any attention to me...\NWhy would you not pay attention to your own sister?!}Anh còn không để ý tới em ...\NTại sao không nhận ra em gái của mình chứ?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.08,0:04:33.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{Uh, well, I...}À ... thì ...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.75,0:04:36.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Th-this is bad. We have to do something.}T-Tệ rồi. Phải làm gì đó thôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.38,0:04:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{Just die, you idiot of a brother!}Chết đi, đồ anh trai ngu ngốc!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.08,0:04:41.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Looks like Bomba's already done for.}Trông Bomba vô vọng rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.96,0:04:43.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{Kirie.}Kirie.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.83,0:04:45.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{Yes, Master?!}Sư phụ?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.58,0:04:48.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{Let's relax and have some cola.}Uống cola và hạ nhiệt chút đi.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.58,0:04:50.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{You too, Bomba.}Bomba nữa.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.00,0:04:56.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{ZO GUTE!\NSo cute!}Dễ thương quá!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.17,0:05:00.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Yeah, they're related all right.}Họ đúng là anh em mà.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.17,0:05:04.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{Hey, how about the four of us play a game?}Vậy sao 4 chúng ta không chơi game nhỉ?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.29,0:05:07.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{Ooh, nice! What do you say\Nwe play on the same team, Kirie?}Hay đó! Em nghĩ sao nếu \Nchúng ta cùng 1 đội, Kirie?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.67,0:05:10.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{G-give me a break! I'm not teaming up with YOU!}Đ-Đừng có đùa! Em sẽ không cùng đội với anh!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.42,0:05:20.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{Umaru, I'm going to the Nyaon Mall\Nto buy groceries for dinner. You need anything?}Umaru. Anh định tới Nyaon để mua đồ.\NEm cần mua gì không?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.88,0:05:24.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{This week's issue of Fanitsu! It's got all the latest! news!}Tập mới của Fanitsu! \NNó có những thông tin mới nhất!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.92,0:05:26.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{Huh? Wait, the bookstore?}Tiệm sách à?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.29,0:05:30.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{It's supposed to rain. I wouldn't want it to get wet.}Sắp mưa rồi, và anh không muốn sách bị ướt.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.58,0:05:34.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{Nah, it'll be fine. Going by this weather,\Nit's not gonna rain.}Không sao đâu. Trông thế chứ còn lâu mới mưa.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.83,0:05:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{You think?}Vậy à?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.63,0:05:44.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{I need to go over today's route!}Xác định đường đi cho hôm nay!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.00,0:05:46.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{It's currently 1:00 pm.}Hiện đang là 1 giờ chiều.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.46,0:05:51.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{The groceries will get heavy, and there's also\Nthe problem of keeping them fresh...\i1}Đồ ăn sẽ nặng, và cũng cần giữ chúng tươi.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.75,0:05:55.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{I'll do the bookstore first. I'll wrap up my purchases\Nat the 3rd-floor bookstore by 1:30.\i1}Mình sẽ đi mua sách trước. \NMọi thứ sẽ xong lúc 1h30.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.29,0:06:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{After that, I'll hurry down to the 1st-floor ATM.\NI'll take note of the crowds and act accordingly,\i1}Sau đó, nhanh chóng xuống ATM ở tầng 1.\NCần chú ý đám đông ở đó,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.25,0:06:05.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{making a careful selection of requisite ingredients.}mua những thứ cần thiết ở siêu thị.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.67,0:06:12.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{The weather will likely make a turn for the worst\Nbetween 3:00 pm and 4:00 pm.\i1}Thời tiết chắc chắn sẽ xấu đi lúc 3h-4h.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.67,0:06:15.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{So, I'll finish up my purchases and get home before then.}Mình sẽ hoàn thành mua đồ trước lúc đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.29,0:06:21.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{Still, this is the same route as always,\Nwith the exception of the bookstore.\i1}Nói vậy nhưng vẫn như mọi ngày,\N trừ việc phải qua tiệm sách.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.21,0:06:25.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{This is the first time I've come to the 3rd floor.}Lần đầu mình lên tầng 3 đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.38,0:06:34.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{Where do they keep the Fanitsu?\NSomewhere near the kids' section?\i1}Fanitsu ở chỗ nào nhỉ? \NLiệu chúng có gần khu sách trẻ em?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.63,0:06:40.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{No, it wouldn't be with the storybooks...}Không ở chỗ sách truyện đâu nhỉ ...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.04,0:06:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{Oh, Kirie.}Kirie.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.17,0:06:45.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{H-hi!}O-Onii...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.67,0:06:47.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{You buying something?}Em đi mua đồ à?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.79,0:06:51.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{N-no! Just browsing! Well, see you!}K-Không ạ, em chỉ lướt qua thôi!\NEm xin phép!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.00,0:06:56.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Maybe that was a bad time to try to talk to her again...}Có vẻ vẫn chưa bắt chuyện với em ấy được ...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.71,0:07:09.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{What was all that about?\NThe same thing happened last time too.\i1}Vậy là sao nhỉ? Lần trước cũng như vậy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.88,0:07:17.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Huh? Kirie...?}Ủa? Kirie?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.25,0:07:20.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{Oh, I get it. Because of the rain.}A, do trời mua à.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.17,0:07:23.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{It's not gonna rain!}Sẽ không mưa đâu!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.75,0:07:26.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{It's freaking pouring down, Umaru...}Đang mưa đó, Umaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.17,0:07:30.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{Hi, Kirie.}Kirie.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.33,0:07:32.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{Oh, Taihei!}O-Onii-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.21,0:07:34.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{Looks like you don't have an umbrella ei...}Có vẻ em không mang ô ...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.25,0:07:37.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{Huh?!}Hể?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.08,0:07:40.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{Wh-what's the matter, Kirie?}S-Sao vậy, Kirie?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.38,0:07:42.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{N-no, it's just...}K-Không có gì, chỉ là ...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.79,0:07:46.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{Come to think of it,\Nshe seems to get a little down on rainy days.\i1}Nhắc mới nhớ, trông em ấy hơi\N chán nản vào những ngày mưa.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.83,0:08:01.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{I... There's something I'd like to do. In the future.}Trong tương lai ... có một điều em muốn làm.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.38,0:08:06.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{I came to the bookstore to do a bit of research, but I...}Em đã tới nhà sách để tham khảo, nhưng ...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.13,0:08:09.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{you always made the best grades in school, didn't you? (Engsub hơi sai thì phải?)}...nhận ra rằng sự thật rất khó khăn.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.33,0:08:24.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{But I'm nowhere near as good as you.\NThere's no way I could make my dream come...}Onii-san luôn làm tốt lúc đi học đúng không? Đó là mục tiêu của em, nhưng lại không làm được.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.21,0:08:30.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{Ah! I'm sorry. You don't want to hear\Nabout any of this, do you?}E-Em xin lỗi! Nghe vậy phiền lắm phải không?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.67,0:08:31.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{No, that's not true at all.}Không đâu.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.58,0:08:35.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{I think you're pretty great, Kirie.}Kirie, anh nghĩ em rất tuyệt.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.92,0:08:37.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{H-huh?!}V-Vâng?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.04,0:08:41.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{True, all I did in high school was study...}Đúng là khi trung học anh đã làm rất tốt.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.63,0:08:47.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{and, yeah, it paid off. But I never\Nthought about what I'd do in the future.}Nhưng kết quả là chẳng biết \Ntương lai sẽ làm gì.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.50,0:08:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{I just stuck to the "route" that was right in front of me.}Anh luôn đi theo con đường đã định sẵn.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.63,0:08:53.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{I guess it's still sort of the same.}Có lẽ bây giờ vẫn như vậy thôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.46,0:08:59.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{I-I... want to be a storybook author.}E-Em muốn trở thành tác giả vẽ truyện.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.29,0:09:03.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{I'm writing a book about my Master.}E-Em đang vẽ truyện về Sư phụ.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.67,0:09:04.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Hả?{Huh?}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.50,0:09:10.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{M-meeting her has made me so happy,\Nand has given me courage.}G-Gặp sư phụ làm em rất vui,\Nnhờ vậy mà em mới có dũng khí.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.96,0:09:14.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{That's why, I want to share that with people everywhere!}Vì vậy, em muốn chia sẻ điều này với mọi người.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.63,0:09:17.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{To tell people about my Master, through storybooks!}Kể cho họ nghe về Sư phụ!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.75,0:09:23.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{You'd be the only one who could do that huh, Kirie?}Chỉ có em mới làm được nhỉ?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.46,0:09:27.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{Yes!}Vâng!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.46,0:09:33.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{Hey, Big Brother!}Onii-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.96,0:09:36.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{Umaru!}Umaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.92,0:09:43.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{I-I feel bad. I told you\Nthat you wouldn't need an umbrella...}E-Em thấy hối hận khi nói vậy ...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.08,0:09:48.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{Don't worry about it.\NAnd I'm glad you brought one for Kirie.}Không sao đâu. May mà \Nem mang thêm 1 cái cho Kirie.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.08,0:09:51.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{Hm? You happy about something, Brother?}Ủa, có chuyện gì vui à Onii-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.17,0:09:56.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{I guess. I was just thinking,\Nit's nice to take a different route sometimes.}Có lẽ vậy. Lâu lâu đổi hướng đi chút cũng vui.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.67,0:09:59.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{Huh? We're going down the same street as always.}Chẳng phải vẫn như mọi khi à?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.42,0:10:01.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{That's not what I mean. Like, the bookstore...}Ý anh không phải vậy, là hiệu sách đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.88,0:10:03.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{Oh, that's right. My Fanitsu!}À đúng rồi, Fanitsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.08,0:10:04.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{Oops.}Chết...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.83,0:10:07.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{Eh? You didn't buy it?!}Hể?! Anh không mua à?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.42,0:10:11.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{I was so concerned about Kirie that I forgot all about it...}Quan tâm tới Kirie quá làm mình quên mất ...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.54,0:10:14.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{Hey, c'mon what the heck?!}Này Onii-chan?!
