Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.50,0:18:19.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{You're eating sweet bread AGAIN?!}Em lại ăn bánh ngọt à?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.71,0:18:21.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{No, I am not!}E-Em không có ăn.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.67,0:18:25.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{Liar! Eating only bread is not healthy at all!}Nói dối. Ăn bánh ngọt suốt ngày không tốt đâu.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.25,0:18:31.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{And here I was thinking you'd be lonely at home\Nby yourself and got you a present...}Chị thì tưởng em cô đơn một mình\Nnên có quà cho em này.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.46,0:18:34.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{A present?! Yes, I want that!}Quà?! Em muốn lắm!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.04,0:18:37.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{Here. It's a stuffed toy cat.}Đây, mèo nhồi bông.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.88,0:18:39.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{It's cute, right?}Đáng yêu đúng không?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.92,0:18:41.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{It is?}Đáng yêu?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.25,0:18:43.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{Huh? Wh-why wouldn't it be cute?}Hể?! Đúng vậy mà?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.88,0:18:46.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{Did you buy this?}Onee-chan mua nó à?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.33,0:18:48.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{O-of course I did.}Đ-Đúng vậy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.33,0:18:51.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{My sister is a little strange.}Onee-chan có hơi lạ.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.96,0:18:56.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{THIS is the sort of thing she likes?}Đây là thứ Onee-chan thích à?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.88,0:18:58.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{I'm home.}Chị về rồi đây.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.25,0:19:00.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{Welcome back...!}Mừng chị v...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.83,0:19:03.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{Sorry for the intrusion.}Xin lỗi vì đã làm phiền.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.83,0:19:10.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{Th-this is my little sister, Hikari.}Đây là em gái của mình, Hikari.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.88,0:19:15.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{You'd mentioned you had a sister.\NShe looks just like MY little sister.}Mình có nhớ cậu từng nhắc tới em gái.\NTrông y hệt em gái mình vậy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.50,0:19:19.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{It's nice to meet you, Hikari.}Rất vui được làm quen, Hikari.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.92,0:19:26.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{Hey, look, Taihei! Here's that recipe book,\Nthe one you said you wanted.}Đây này Taihei, quyển công thức\N nấu ăn hôm nọ cậu muốn đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.13,0:19:30.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{Thank you. What are the odds\Nyou'd have this very same book?}Cảm ơn cậu nhiều. Đúng là trùng hợp\Nkhi cậu có một quyển đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.67,0:19:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{I-it's my pleasure! My way of thanking you\Nfor that stuffed doll!}K-Không sao đâu! Coi như lời \Ncảm ơn cho con mèo nhồi bông đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.67,0:19:37.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{I looked around, but just couldn't seem to find this book.}Mình đã tìm suốt mà không thấy cuốn sách này.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.54,0:19:38.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{I can't believe you had it.}May mà cậu có nó.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.04,0:19:41.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{Oh, it was pure coincidence!}Chỉ là vô tình thôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.50,0:19:43.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{So this is...}Thì ra đây là ...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.33,0:19:46.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{my sister's type!}Người Onee-chan thích!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.13,0:19:49.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{Well, I don't want to inconvenience you\Nby staying too long.}Mình xin phép nhé, không muốn làm phiền cậu lâu.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.54,0:19:51.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{Oh, w-well, okay!}C-Cũng đúng nhỉ.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.04,0:19:54.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{Um!}À...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.17,0:19:57.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{Please have some of my sister's cooking!}Hãy ăn thử món của chị ấy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.54,0:19:59.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{Her cooking?}Món ăn?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.00,0:20:08.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{I never knew your sister was good in the kitchen.}Anh không biết là Kanau giỏi nấu ăn đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.38,0:20:20.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{Looks like this will take a little while...}Có vẻ hơi tốn thời gian rồi...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.96,0:20:22.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{The stars are so pretty!}Những ngôi sao ... Đẹp ghê!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.33,0:20:26.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{Oh, you're right. You can really see them, huh?}Đúng vậy. Có thể nhìn rõ nhỉ?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.88,0:20:30.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{Well, how about I teach you\Nthe constellations' names to pass the time?}Vậy để anh dạy em về tên  \Nnhững ngôi sao trong lúc chờ nhé?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.13,0:20:33.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{Huh? Their names?}Tên chúng ạ?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.38,0:20:34.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{Yeah.}Ừm.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.25,0:20:38.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{First off, that's Cassiopeia.\NThe stars are lined up in a "W" shape, see?}Đầu tiên, đó là chòm Thiên Hậu.\NNhững ngôi sao được xếp thành hình chữ W.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.04,0:20:42.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{My sister is strange...\Nand she brought home a strange guy.\i1}Onee-chan lạ thật ... và chị ấy \Ndẫn một anh trai cũng kì lạ về.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.58,0:20:45.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{He's my big brother!}Đây là Onii-chan của Hikari!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.75,0:20:47.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{Blgh!}Hả?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.00,0:20:51.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{I'm sorry, Hikari. I'd totally forgotten.}Xin lỗi nhé Hikari. Anh quên mất.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.38,0:20:53.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{No, it's okay. I'm really happy.}Không sao đâu. Em vui lắm.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.88,0:20:57.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{Thank you for remembering... Big Brother!}Cảm ơn vì anh đã nhớ, Onii-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.79,0:21:01.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{I've missed you so much!}Em nhớ anh lắm!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.92,0:21:05.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{Jeez! How long are you gonna keep this up?!\NThis is MY big...}Định diễn bao lâu nữa vậy?! Onii-chan ...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.38,0:21:10.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{Um...}À...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.79,0:21:11.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{Huh?}Hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.63,0:21:15.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{With the both of you on me, I can't really move...}2 đứa ... Anh không di chuyển được.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.75,0:21:18.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{Yeah, that's right! The "Dive" is MY technique!}Đúng rồi đó! Dive là tuyệt kĩ của Umaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.17,0:21:20.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{It's a technique?}Tuyệt kĩ à?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.79,0:21:23.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{I have my own technique, the Hikari Dive!}Hikari cũng có Hikari Dive!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.33,0:21:24.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{The Hikari Dive?}Hikari Dive?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.88,0:21:27.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{First thing's first: Get off of him!}Tóm lại là rời khỏi người anh ấy đi Hikari!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.79,0:21:30.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{No. Rotation-wise, this is my turn.}Không. Theo chiều thì đây là lượt của mình.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.42,0:21:31.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{How dare y-?!}Sao cậu ...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.42,0:21:32.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{I dare!}Cậu đó!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.96,0:21:37.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{I guess this is what a mother feels like...}Đây là cảm giác của một người mẹ ...?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.04,0:21:41.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{It's really okay? Just taking you this far...}Có ổn không nếu chỉ đưa em tới đây ...?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.17,0:21:43.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{Yes, I've got someone coming for me.}Vâng. Sẽ có người tới đón em.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.79,0:21:45.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{All right then, Hikari.}Vậy nhé, Hikari.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.04,0:21:50.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{See you soon.}Gặp lại sau.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.00,0:21:54.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{Okay!}Ừm!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.83,0:23:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{This will be the last episode, huh everyone?}Sắp tập cuối rồi nhỉ?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.00,0:23:30.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{Looking back, it's gone by so fast.}Nhìn lại thì cũng nhanh thật,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.83,0:23:34.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{Indeed, it feels like a mere three months have passed!}Đúng là chẳng có cảm giác gì là đã trôi qua 3 tháng.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.04,0:23:35.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{It's a little sad, isn't it?}Hơi buồn nhỉ?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.71,0:23:38.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{Okay, let's finish this out, everyone. One, two...}Cùng kết thúc nào mọi người. 1, 2 ...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.38,0:23:40.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{See you again, indeed!\NSee you again!}Hẹn gặp lại!
